title: [15 Plat IV German/English] Lookin for a Team IGN: Nykuu
body:
Hey ppl my name is Niklas "Nykuu" I am a Top main 15 years old and currently sittin in plat 4 I mainly speak German, but my English is not to bad. 
My Toplane pool is pretty big and I think Im a pretty solid sololaner, I should be able to take critic :'), so I am currently lookin for a Team speakin' German or English, so if youre interested my IGN: Nykuu
